  <entry>
    <title>B站收藏夹视频导出</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/09/B%E7%AB%99%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%A4%B9%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/09/B%E7%AB%99%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%A4%B9%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这里给出两种导出方法：一种只保留标题链接，另一种保留封面图片和标题链接，并按照一行5个视频的格式排列（模仿B站的样式）</p><h2 id="只导出标题链接文本"><a href="#只导出标题链接文本" class="headerlink" title="只导出标题链接文本"></a>只导出标题链接文本</h2><p>参考：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/toumingbai/p/11399238.html">快速导出B站收藏单节目列表 - 鱼肉真好吃 - 博客园 (cnblogs.com)</a></p><p>这里对代码稍作修改，将标题和链接合并。</p><p>使用方法和上述参考博客的方法一样，先进入收藏夹页面（网站链接形如 <code>https://space.bilibili.com/xxxxxxxx/favlist?fid=xxxxxxxx</code>），然后按 <code>F12</code>进入开发者界面，在控制台复制下段代码：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">get_list</span> ()<br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> result = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>;<br>    $(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.fav-video-list &gt; li &gt;a.title&quot;</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">each</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)&#123;<br>        result += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&lt;a href=&quot;&#x27;</span> + $(<span class="hljs-variable language_">this</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">attr</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;href&quot;</span>) + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&quot; target=_blank &gt;&#x27;</span> + $(<span class="hljs-variable language_">this</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">text</span>() + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#x27;</span>;<br>    &#125;);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> result;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> html = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span> ()&#123;<br>    html += <span class="hljs-title function_">get_list</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>($(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.be-pager-next:visible&quot;</span>).<span class="hljs-property">length</span> == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>    &#123;   <br>        <span class="hljs-variable language_">document</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">write</span>(html);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>&#123;<br>        $(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.be-pager-next&quot;</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">click</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">setTimeout</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;main()&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">5000</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-title function_">main</span>();<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序运行完后，会生成HTML网页，按 <code>Ctrl+S</code>即可保存到本地。保存后的效果如下：</p><p><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://article.biliimg.com/bfs/article/14c21499e15c075623d01af04d13c6580e8fbacf.png"></p><h2 id="导出带封面图片的链接表格"><a href="#导出带封面图片的链接表格" class="headerlink" title="导出带封面图片的链接表格"></a>导出带封面图片的链接表格</h2><p>使用Python脚本编写爬虫爬取收藏夹的图片和标题链接，代码如下：</p><p>【注】请将代码中的cookie和user-agent更换为自己电脑的参数，获取方式如下：</p><ul><li>按 <code>F12</code>进入开发者界面，点击 <code>网络</code>标签页</li><li>在搜索栏输入 <code>json</code>，并按 <code>Ctrl+R</code>刷新</li><li>找到名称形如 <code>list?media_id=xxxxxxxx&amp;pn=1&amp;ps=20</code>的候选项（通常是最后一个），点击 <code>标头</code>标签页，即可在 <code>请求标头</code>中找到cookie和user-agent参数</li><li>将代码中的参数替换为自己的参数</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> requests<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> json<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> time<br><br>headers = &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cookie&quot;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;更改为自己的cookie参数&quot;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;user-agent&quot;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;更改为自己的user-agent参数&quot;</span><br>&#125;<br><br>fav_id = <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入收藏夹ID: &quot;</span>))<br>page_max = <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入收藏夹的页数: &quot;</span>))<br><br>info_title = <span class="hljs-literal">None</span><br>output_doc = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>col_count = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> page_index <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(page_max):<br>    url = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://api.bilibili.com/x/v3/fav/resource/list?media_id=&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(fav_id) + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&amp;pn=&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(page_index + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&amp;ps=20&amp;keyword=&amp;order=mtime&amp;type=0&amp;tid=0&amp;platform=web&amp;jsonp=jsonp&quot;</span><br>    data_text = requests.get(url=url, headers=headers).text<br>    data = json.loads(data_text)<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 列表一行开始</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> col_count == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>        output_doc += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&lt;tr&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 录入一页信息</span><br>    info_title = data[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;data&quot;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;info&quot;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;title&quot;</span>]<br>    medias = data[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;data&quot;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;medias&quot;</span>]<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> media <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> medias:<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 一行放置5个视频</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> col_count &lt; <span class="hljs-number">5</span>:<br>            output_doc += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t\t&lt;td&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>            col_count += <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            output_doc += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&lt;/tr&gt;\n\t&lt;tr&gt;\n\t\t&lt;td&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>            col_count = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 输入图片和标题链接</span><br>        output_doc = output_doc + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t\t\t&lt;img src=&quot;&#x27;</span> + media[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;cover&quot;</span>] + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&quot; height=108 width=192/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>        output_doc = output_doc + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t\t\t&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bilibili.com/video/&#x27;</span> + media[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bv_id&quot;</span>] + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> + media[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;title&quot;</span>] + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&lt;/a&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br>      <br>        output_doc += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\n&#x27;</span><br><br>    time.sleep(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br><br>output_doc += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;&#x27;</span><br>info_title += <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.html&#x27;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(info_title, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> f:<br>    f.write(output_doc)<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码运行完会生成与收藏夹同名的HTML文件，用浏览器打开即可。导出的效果如下：</p><p><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://article.biliimg.com/bfs/article/5dfcf7483414c4f2abb7920d0d888bb919d99d2e.png"></p><p>【注】该HTML文件中的图片是网页链接，每次打开都需要加载。可以用浏览器打开后按 <code>Ctrl+S</code>保存成带文件夹的HTML文件（图片都下载到文件夹中）或mhtml文件（图片嵌入文件中，无需加载）</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
